{
  "_comment": "Synthetic n8n-style export. Reproduces the shapes that caused false positives in a real pasted workflow, with no personal content. n8n exports credential REFERENCES (id + name), never the tokens themselves, so nothing here is a secret.",
  "name": "Example Workflow",
